<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='481000' id='t-481000'>They have come up with, in a sense, a different method for organizing activity.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486000' id='t-486000'>The Yale Law professor Yochai Benkler, in an essay called &quot;Coase's Penguin,&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='491000' id='t-491000'>talks about this open-source model, which we're familiar with from Linux,</span>
