<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='498000' id='t-498000'>And, you know, if you think about this with the tsunami,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='500000' id='t-500000'>what you have is essentially a kind of an army of local journalists,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='504000' id='t-504000'>who are producing enormous amounts of material</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='507000' id='t-507000'>for no reason other than to tell their stories.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509000' id='t-509000'>That's a very powerful idea, and it's a very powerful reality.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='513000' id='t-513000'>And it's one that offers really interesting possibilities</span>
