</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='521000' id='t-521000'>So, I think the first thing that the blogosphere tells us</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='524000' id='t-524000'>is that we need to expand our idea of what counts as rational,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='527000' id='t-527000'>and we need to expand our simple equation of value equals money,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531000' id='t-531000'>or, you have to pay for it to be good,</span>
