<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='556000' id='t-556000'>but this notion of voluntary cooperation</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='559000' id='t-559000'>is an incredibly powerful one, and one worth thinking about.</span>
