<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='596000' id='t-596000'>your average guess would be remarkably good.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='599000' id='t-599000'>It would be somewhere probably within three and five percent</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='601000' id='t-601000'>of the number of beans in the jar,</span>
