<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='616000' id='t-616000'>And what's fascinating is that you can see this phenomenon at work</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='619000' id='t-619000'>in many more complicated situations.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:33
</data>
