<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='663000' id='t-663000'>Dan Gillmor -- whose book &quot;We the Media&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='665000' id='t-665000'>is included in the gift pack --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='667000' id='t-667000'>has talked about it as saying that, as a writer,</span>
