<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='739000' id='t-739000'>and we're able to access information that has always been there</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='742000' id='t-742000'>but has essentially gone untapped.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:36
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='745000' id='t-745000'>But there is a dark side to this,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='747000' id='t-747000'>and that's what I want to spend the last part of my talk on.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='750000' id='t-750000'>One of the things that happens if you spend a lot of time on the Internet,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='753000' id='t-753000'>and you spend a lot of time thinking about the Internet,</span>
