<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='879000' id='t-879000'>and it is one that essentially throws off</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='882000' id='t-882000'>this beautiful, decentralized, bottom-up intelligence</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='885000' id='t-885000'>that blogs can manifest in the right conditions.</span>
