<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='961000' id='t-961000'>Now, I want to connect this back, though, to the tsunami,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='964000' id='t-964000'>because one of the great things about the tsunami --</span>
