<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='968000' id='t-968000'>not in terms of the tsunami itself --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='970000' id='t-970000'>is that it really did represent a genuine bottom-up phenomenon.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='974000' id='t-974000'>You saw sites that had never existed before getting huge amounts of traffic.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='977000' id='t-977000'>You saw people being able to offer up
